column5: Headed up Friday, curious what people are seeing for water temp on the east side? Thanks
We were up in the Canoe Bay and Grassy Bay area last week. The water temp. varied between 67-70.
Went for a swim last week....nipples like bullets!
ANy fishing reports for the east side of lac seul? Going to be taking out 10 guys with 4 greenhorns on one of those houseboats Sunday and just wanted to see what's shaking up that way.
